comments: Miller's (CHA) hands come forward prior to marginal contact occurring with LeVert's (CLE) upper body during the drive.
Williams' (CHA) right forearm comes forward prior to marginal contact occurring with LeVert's (CLE) front at the end of the drive.
Bridges (CHA) cleanly deflects the ball away from Mobley (CLE) as the pass is made.
Allen (CLE) initiates contact with Williams' (CHA) head during Williams' upward shooting motion.
Allen (CLE) establishes himself in Mann's (CHA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Allen (CLE) establishes himself in Mann's (CHA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Mann (CHA) and Allen (CLE) engage and disengage with one another off-ball, and marginal contact occurs.
Mann (CHA) initiates contact across Allen's (CLE) right wrist, subsequently allowing Mann to then make contact with the ball thereafter during Allen's upward shooting motion.
Okoro (CLE) initiates contact across Williams' (CHA) front and affects Williams' SQBR during the drive.
LeVert (CLE) does not inbound the ball within five seconds.
Micic (CHA) and Merrill (CLE) engage and disengage with one another off-ball, and marginal contact occurs.
Bridges (CHA) is moving forward slightly as LeVert (CLE) cuts back toward the basket and marginal body contact occurs when they come together in the lane.
LeVert (CLE) gathers the ball on his right foot and establishes his left foot as his pivot, which he slides as he comes to a stop in the lane.
LeVert (CLE) turns slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Micic (CHA) near midcourt.
Williams (CHA) establishes himself in Allen's (CLE) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Mann (CHA) lands short of Strus (CLE) after contesting the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs as a result of Strus' momentum carrying him forward toward Mann upon returning to the floor.
